WEBVTT

00:00.828 --> 00:05.631
And Community Play is about
more than just providing gyms.

00:06.700 --> 00:09.702
It's about building bridges
between law enforcement

00:09.727 --> 00:11.261
and at-risk kids.

00:11.286 --> 00:12.587
It's a place where kids get to know

00:12.621 --> 00:14.488
the person behind the badge.

00:14.523 --> 00:17.692
And police aren't making
arrests and asking questions.

00:17.726 --> 00:21.406
Instead they're giving their
perspectives on leadership,

00:22.197 --> 00:24.985
conflict resolution, empathy,

00:25.243 --> 00:27.511
and most importantly, trust.

00:27.536 --> 00:31.539
Community Play thrives
on good folks like you.

00:31.573 --> 00:33.174
And when I say good folks,

00:33.208 --> 00:35.710
I mean caring, compassionate people

00:35.744 --> 00:37.845
who are also willing
to open those wallets.

00:42.491 --> 00:45.026
You know, earlier tonight
I was taking a little walk

00:45.053 --> 00:48.689
on beautiful streets
here on the North Side.

00:48.724 --> 00:50.891
This is the Chicago we all want.

00:50.926 --> 00:54.462
Family friendly. A safe
haven from gun violence.

00:54.496 --> 01:00.034
And with your help, we've made
this little organization

01:00.068 --> 01:02.737
a safe haven as well.

01:02.771 --> 01:05.272
So thank you for coming
tonight, and God bless.

01:07.009 --> 01:08.643
Thank you.

01:08.677 --> 01:10.544
Yo, let's get out of here
and get a real drink.

01:10.579 --> 01:12.747
Hey, how are Vinessa and Jordan doing?

01:12.781 --> 01:14.482
They're actually doing pretty good.

01:14.516 --> 01:16.917
I told 'em though, if
they become Cowboys fans,

01:16.952 --> 01:18.452
they can't come back.

01:18.487 --> 01:20.788
- Is that a possibility?
- You wanna roll?

01:20.822 --> 01:22.657
We're off the clock in ten minutes.

01:22.691 --> 01:24.091
Unless you know another place

01:24.126 --> 01:26.093
serving free Chantal de Laroque?

01:26.128 --> 01:29.630
Wow. You're really um...
Oh what's the word?

01:29.665 --> 01:31.499
Le snob.

01:31.533 --> 01:33.401
The Lake Forest in me escaping.

01:33.435 --> 01:35.136
What? I thought you were from Greektown.

01:35.170 --> 01:37.238
That's just a story I tell in bars.

01:37.272 --> 01:38.506
- Hmm.
- Just kidding.

01:38.540 --> 01:41.275
We moved there when I was 11.

01:45.347 --> 01:46.814
You know that guy?

01:46.848 --> 01:49.984
Yeah. Sean McGrady.
Sergeant out of narcotics.

01:50.018 --> 01:51.419
Couple years back

01:51.453 --> 01:53.254
I was assigned to
his joint investigation.

01:53.288 --> 01:54.455
Good police.

01:54.489 --> 01:56.824
She says with hesitation.

01:56.858 --> 01:58.526
No, he is. He's just...

01:58.560 --> 02:03.097
Competitive. Always looking
for an angle. Drove me nuts.

02:03.131 --> 02:05.833
Hank! Glad you came.

02:05.867 --> 02:07.468
I appreciate all the time and effort

02:07.502 --> 02:09.470
your team has put in around here.

02:09.503 --> 02:12.106
It's a good cause. Happy to help.

02:12.140 --> 02:13.774
It's a hell of a shindig.

02:13.809 --> 02:15.976
Well, you got to
spend money to make money.

02:16.011 --> 02:16.977
Mm.

02:18.647 --> 02:20.514
Sean, we need to talk about this!

02:20.549 --> 02:21.949
- Oh you want to talk?
- Yeah. Tonight!

02:21.983 --> 02:23.718
You want to talk about this now?

02:23.752 --> 02:26.387
- What, are you out of your mind?
- Hey! Hey! Whoa!

02:26.421 --> 02:28.289
- What's going on?
- No, we're good.

02:28.323 --> 02:31.459
Right? We're good.

02:31.493 --> 02:34.462
It's good to see you, Hailey.

02:34.496 --> 02:35.963
You okay?

02:35.997 --> 02:38.632
Yeah. It was just a misunderstanding.

02:40.669 --> 02:42.303
We got shots fired nearby.

02:42.337 --> 02:44.371
- Active shooter.
- Okay.

