- I've got it.
- Stairs.

03:06.027 --> 03:07.762
I got two down!

03:07.796 --> 03:09.130
Cover me.

03:14.603 --> 03:17.171
- Anything?
- They're both gone.

03:28.550 --> 03:31.118
He got a pulse. Call an ambo.

03:31.153 --> 03:33.788
This is 5021 Charlie.
Roll an ambo to our location.

03:33.822 --> 03:36.056
3 GSWs, one still breathing.

03:36.091 --> 03:39.693
Nine mil casings. Male takes
one to the back of the head.

03:39.728 --> 03:41.228
Female takes two to the chest.

03:41.263 --> 03:42.897
Dad gets beat, then popped.

03:42.931 --> 03:44.632
Wife walks in. Goodbye witness.

03:44.666 --> 03:46.200
Son Ryan, he's hiding out
in the bathroom.

03:46.234 --> 03:48.202
Killer finds him.
He takes two to the chest.

03:48.236 --> 03:49.637
Anything on the victims yet?

03:49.671 --> 03:52.706
Yeah. Grant Hammond,
wife Margaret, son Ryan.

03:52.741 --> 03:54.809
Grant was a corporate attorney.

03:54.843 --> 03:56.443
Looks like he spent a lot of
time at his church.

03:56.478 --> 03:58.546
Hey. I think we found what the killers

03:58.580 --> 04:00.681
were looking for upstairs.

04:04.920 --> 04:06.887
Praise the Lord.

04:06.922 --> 04:09.557
Two keys. That's about
200 grand street value.

04:09.591 --> 04:11.559
I've seen guys kill over a lot less.

04:11.593 --> 04:13.704
So much for the safe haven
of the North Side.

